<div id="review_3446278299" class="review nosyndicate" itemprop="reviews" itemscope itemtype="http://schema.org/Review">
  <link itemprop="url" href="https://www.goodreads.com/review/show/3446278299" />
    <a title="Patti" class="left imgcol" href="/user/show/1913087-patti"><img alt="Patti" src="https://s.gr-assets.com/assets/nophoto/user/f_50x66-6a03a5c12233c941481992b82eea8d23.png" /></a>

  <div class="left bodycol">
    <div class="reviewHeader uitext stacked">
        <a class="reviewDate createdAt right" href="/review/show/3446278299?book_show_action=true">Jul 16, 2020</a>

      <span itemprop="author" itemscope itemtype="http://schema.org/Person">
        <a title="Patti" class="user" itemprop="url" name="Patti" href="/user/show/1913087-patti">Patti</a>
      </span>

        rated it
        <span class=" staticStars notranslate" title="really liked it"><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10">really liked it</span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p0"></span></span>

          <span class="greyText">&nbsp;&middot;&nbsp;</span>
          <a class="lightGreyText" title="Hardcover 9780884948537" href="/book/show/1153922.Truth_Will_Prevail">review of another edition</a>


        

    </div>


        <div class="reviewText stacked">
              <span id="reviewTextContainer3446278299" class="readable"
              >
            
<span id="freeTextContainer10124237590391921839">So far, ‘Truth Will Prevail’ #3 has been my favorite so far: 4½ stars. This one covers 1836-1838. What I liked so much is that we really get to know the characters, fictional and real, in great detail. I feel invested in each one! <br/><br/>After spending so much time disliking Joshua in books #1 &amp; #2, I actually found myself coming around to having hope for him. I realize he’s fictional, but many real people could identify with his strong feelings against his family. <br/><br/>On to #4…<br/></span>

          </span>
        </div>


